Sometimes we just need someone to help bring out what’s been inside of us.

I kept replaying over and over in my head how I was going to get unstuck and breathe what was inside of me all along.  Going back and forth with “Alright Imma do it” and “Well I better just wait cause this and that ain’t right yet” just full of excuses, impostor syndrome and perfection.  These things coupled had me sleeping on myself!

I got an Accountability Partner/Coach who believed in me just as much as I did and WANTED to see me win, pushed me out of my comfort zone, gave me resources that I thought was out of my reach and celebrated my small wins!  It was literally a breath of fresh air and the fire I needed at the same time.

Let me remind you that “Strength courage and wisdom, it’s been inside of you all along” ~ You might just need someone to help you use it.

#ladylerose #musicjourney #momandwife #accountability #accountabilitycoach #transparency

Things I do to pour back into myself‼️

Normalizing Self-Love and Self-Care came at a pivotal time in my life. I was so dedicated to being an awesome mom, wife, sister, daughter and friend, that I forgot to tend to myself.

It wasn’t that I regretted being the best I could be to everyone around me, the problem came when I didn’t consider me just as important.

What are some things that you’ve done or NEED TO DO to pour back into yourself? 🤨

No matter how small of an adjustment is needed, DO IT!  Yourself will thank you 🌹
